	\chapter{System Design and Methodology}
	\label{chap:design}
	
	This chapter presents the software architecture of the proposed RAG-based multimodal system
	for periapical dental radiograph analysis and clinical decision support.
	Section~\ref{sec:dsr} outlines the Design Science Research methodology.
	Section~\ref{sec:architecture} introduces the overall three-stage sequential pipeline and
	justifies its design. Section~\ref{sec:components} details each core system component.
	Section~\ref{sec:workflow} traces the complete data flow and documents the API and database
	design. Section~\ref{sec:multi_provider} describes the multi provider integration strategy
