	\subsection{Vision Analysis Layer}
	\label{sec:vision}
	
	The vision analysis layer provides a unified interface to multiple vision model providers
	through the \texttt{VisionClient} abstraction class. The layer abstracts all
	provider-specific details behind a common interface, keeping the orchestration engine
	entirely agnostic to the underlying model. Ten vision models are supported across local and
	cloud providers (Table~\ref{tab:vision_providers}).

	
	
	% -----------------
	
	\begin{table}[h]
		\centering
		\caption{Supported vision model providers and key characteristics.}
		\label{tab:vision_providers}
