			Gemma3          & gemma3:4b, gemma3:12b        & Ollama (local)     & 2.5\,GB / 8.1\,GB \\
			LLaVA-Med       & llava-med                    & Ollama (local)     & 7.4\,GB \\
			Llama 3.2-Vision& llama3.2-vision              & Ollama (local)     & 7.9\,GB \\
			BiomedCLIP      & BiomedCLIP-PubMedBERT        & open\_clip (local) & 0.5\,GB \\
			Florence-2      & Florence-2-base              & HuggingFace (local)& 1.6\,GB \\
			GPT-4V          & gpt-4o                       & OpenAI API         & --- \\
