\subsection{Radiograph Dataset}
\label{subsec:images}

Actual patient radiographs from Tanzanian facilities were unavailable
due to data-protection and consent constraints (acknowledged as a
limitation in Section~\ref{sec:limitations}).  Evaluation therefore relies on
publicly available periapical radiograph images sourced from open
research repositories, filtered for diagnostic quality and permissive
licensing.  A single periapical radiograph was used as the primary test
case for all vision model comparisons, providing a consistent and
controlled baseline for cross-model evaluation.
Table~\ref{tab:test_image} describes the test image and its associated
synthetic clinical presentation.

