Gemini      & $\checkmark$ (severe) & $\checkmark$ & $\checkmark^{\dagger}$ & Severe recurrent caries with large periapical radiolucency & 0.92 \\
Claude      & $\checkmark$ (mod.) & $\checkmark$ & $\checkmark^{\dagger}$ & Moderate caries + periapical + bone loss & 0.70 \\
